  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to sdl2-image</title>

    <para>
      <application>sdl2-image</application> is a simple library to load images of various formats as SDL surfaces.
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
